N2  - Following publication of my paper entitled (Fife, Dennis W. 1965. Scheduling with random arrivals and linear loss functions. Management Sci. 11 (3, January) 429?437.), a private comment on it was received by the Editor. I responded to this, also in a private communication to the Editor. However the Editor has now suggested that a published statement from me would be appropriate to close the matter.
